>>> ---------- Forwarded message ----------
>>> From: Chris Cillizza <Chris.Cillizza@washingtonpost.com>
>>> Date: Thu, May 15, 2008 at 10:54 AM
>>> Subject: Progressive Media USA Ditches Ad Effort
